                            <comment id="13579678" author="billgraham" created="Sat, 16 Feb 2013 02:08:49 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Attaching a patch. Patch doesn&apos;t include deletion of &lt;tt&gt;ivy/pig.pom&lt;/tt&gt; since I can&apos;t seem to get that reflected once the file is deleted. &lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13581296" author="jcoveney" created="Tue, 19 Feb 2013 14:11:37 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Bill, are you using git? git rm file should reflect the deletion. Does it not?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13581297" author="jcoveney" created="Tue, 19 Feb 2013 14:12:17 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Also, +1&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13581406" author="billgraham" created="Tue, 19 Feb 2013 16:22:44 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;tt&gt;git rm&lt;/tt&gt; did not, but just &lt;tt&gt;rm&lt;/tt&gt; did the trick. Here&apos;s patch 2 which reflects the delete.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
